metadata.name: /China Love/
metadata.description:
This piece will be shipped to the highest bidder. A  custom digital art piece, will also be sent to you directly. 

China love - inspired by Janet Jackson is a calming and sensual painting that allows you to feel the morning breeze. 

Dimensions:  24x36
Medium: Acrylic on black canvas,  charcoal 

- for a more detailed view / pictures are posted via twitter.
